=== Practical 8: Power ===


:- initialization(main).

power(_, 0, 1).
power(Num, Pow, Ans) :- Pow > 0, P1 is Pow-1, power(Num, P1, A1), Ans is Num * A1.

main :-
    write('=== Practical Power ==='), nl, nl,
    power(2, 10, R1), write('2^10 = '), write(R1), nl,
    power(5, 3, R2), write('5^3 = '), write(R2), nl,
    power(10, 0, R3), write('10^0 = '), write(R3), nl.


###Output

=== Practical Power ===

2^10 = 1024
5^3 = 125
10^0 = 1
